'''Pho4'''是一种在[[釀酒酵母|釀酒酵母]]（''S. cerevisiae''）中发现的[[碱性螺旋-环-螺旋|碱性螺旋-环-螺旋]]（bHLH）[[转录因子|转录因子]]，在其它酵母中也有发现<ref name="pmid2220078">{{cite journal |vauthors=Berben G, Legrain M, Gilliquet V, Hilger F | title = The yeast regulatory gene PHO4 encodes a helix-loop-helix motif | journal = Yeast | volume = 6 | issue = 5 | pages = 451–4 | year = 1990 | pmid = 2220078 | doi = 10.1002/yea.320060510 }}</ref>

Pho4蛋白形成同源[[蛋白二聚体|二聚体]]后进入[[细胞核|细胞核]]结合[[DNA|DNA]]，其[[结合位点|识别位点]]为：5'-CACGTG-3'<ref name="pmid9443961">{{cite journal |vauthors=Shao D, Creasy CL, Bergman LW | title = A cysteine residue in helixII of the bHLH domain is essential for homodimerization of the yeast transcription factor Pho4p | journal = Nucleic Acids Res. | volume = 26 | issue = 3 | pages = 710–4 |date=February 1998 | pmid = 9443961 | pmc = 147311 | doi = 10.1093/nar/26.3.710 }}</ref>，这一序列常出现在[[Pho5|Pho5]]等[[磷酸酶|磷酸酶]][[基因|基因]]的[[啟動子|啟動子]]区域<ref name="pmid2183025">{{cite journal |vauthors=Ogawa N, Oshima Y | title = Functional domains of a positive regulatory protein, PHO4, for transcriptional control of the phosphatase regulon in Saccharomyces cerevisiae |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-and-cellular-biology_1990-05_10_5/page/2224 | journal = Mol. Cell. Biol. | volume = 10 | issue = 5 | pages = 2224–36 |date=May 1990 | pmid = 2183025 | pmc = 360570 | doi = 10.1128/mcb.10.5.2224}}</ref>。

